name: Mackenzie Global Infrastructure Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible. The Fund before fees and expenses, the performance of the Solactive Global Infrastructure Select Index, or any successor thereto. It invests primarily in equity securities of global infrastructure companies in developed and emerging markets.
